{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/midashi_1_en.png?t=1737698781\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The protagonist, Hiro, visits his relative's house in the countryside by himself.<br>This is a pixel art simulation game where you live under one roof for a month with three sisters, your childhood friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">How you spend your time is up to you!<br>You can fish in the ocean or a river, have your catch cooked, build a secret base...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The village is full of interesting folks, like the fisherman, the candy store owner, and your neighbors. <br>Complete their requests and they might reward you...!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Make this month full of memories of your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/midashi_2_en.png?t=1737698781\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/face_haruka.png?t=1737698781\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Haruka</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The older sister who is always nice to you and great at cooking.<br>Her food is so good, you could never get tired of it. In fact, you always end up overeating...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3449880/extras/face_yui.png?t=1737698781\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Yui</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The closest person in age to you.<br>She's got a ton of toys and knows how to use them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"b